des:
OCTAS-Smart help you control home appliance.You can simply ask Alexa to turn on or turn off your light.
There’s no need to go to the switch to adjust your light - just talk to Alexa on your Amazon Echo.
After connecting Alexa to your OCTAS-Smart in a few simple steps:
(1). Download our "OCTAS-Smart"app in android or ios app market;
(2). Register an account in our "OCTAS-Smart" app;
(3). You need to have some OCTAS-Smart devices in hand;
(4). Configure these devices in our "OCTAS-Smart" app and change appropriate name for your devices which will be used in "OCTAS"skills;
(5). Download Amazon "Alexa"app from android,ios or Amazon app market;
(6). Configure Echo with "Alexa" app;
(7). Search "OCTAS" skill from the "Alexa" app skills category;
(8). Click Enable skill of "OCTAS", and you'll be navigated to OCTAS login page;
(9). Input your OCTAS-Smart account username and password, you'll be redirect to the success page;
(10). Now all setup is finished.
You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices like these:
“Alexa,turn on the bedroom light.”
“Alexa,turn off the bedroom light.”
“Alexa,set the bedroom light to 50%.”
“Alexa,brighten the bedroom light to 50%.”
“Alexa,dim the bedroom light to 50%.”
“Alexa, set bedroom light to green.”
“Alexa, set bedroom light to cool white.”
